What is more, on returning to Ankara â following the negotiations in December 2004 under the Dutch Presidency â Mr Erdogan made it known at once that the signing would certainly not amount to recognition of Cyprus, whether explicit or implicit.
With regard to the Cyprus issue, I take the view that the Council should make every effort to bring about the unification of Cyprus.
